

{"id":4127,"date":"2023-05-24T16:51:55","date_gmt":"2023-05-24T09:51:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=4127"},"modified":"2023-05-29T14:26:54","modified_gmt":"2023-05-29T07:26:54","slug":"calo-la-gi-8-buoc-kiem-soat-calo-giam-can-tang-can","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/calo-la-gi-8-buoc-kiem-soat-calo-de-tang-can-giam-can\/","title":{"rendered":"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec? 8 b\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t Calo \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 8pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em><strong>Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t calo, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec? 8 b\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t calo \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft.\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn c\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0103n ki\u00eang v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n cho\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3p, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch \u0103n u\u1ed1ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nhau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng n\u00e0o l\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo v\u00e0 \u00fd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, The New Gym s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho b\u1ea1n calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0103n bao nhi\u00eau n\u1ebfu m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading--level3 brand-color \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Calo \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4180\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4180\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4180 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/hieu-ve-calo-de-giam-can-1.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/hieu-ve-calo-de-giam-can-1.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/hieu-ve-calo-de-giam-can-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/hieu-ve-calo-de-giam-can-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/hieu-ve-calo-de-giam-can-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/hieu-ve-calo-de-giam-can-1-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/hieu-ve-calo-de-giam-can-1-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4180\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Calo \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea1i The New Gym, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea1n trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. N\u1ebfu m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n ki\u00eang &#8216;c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m&#8217; calo c\u00f3 v\u1ebb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 lu\u00f4n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n khi thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 calo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, gi\u00e0u vi ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ef1c \u0111oan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p theo d\u00f5i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\u00a0N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u00e3y n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129, chuy\u00ean gia dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0103n u\u1ed1ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading--level3 brand-color \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><br \/>\nCalo l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4182\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4182\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4182 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/calo-la-gi-1.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/calo-la-gi-1.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/calo-la-gi-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/calo-la-gi-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/calo-la-gi-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/calo-la-gi-1-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/calo-la-gi-1-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4182\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Calo<\/strong> l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 th\u1ee9c \u0103n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u1eeb n\u00e3o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1eafp tay.\u00a0Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111a l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 protein, carbohydrate v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o &#8211; t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c nhau trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00e1c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c nhau \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3ng <strong>calo<\/strong> n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 ch\u00fang.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading--level3 brand-color \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><br \/>\nL\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n?<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4197\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4197\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4197 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lam-the-nao-de-giam-can-1.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4197\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang ta th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u1ec1u calo h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd t\u00edch tr\u1eef l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o.\u00a0Vi\u1ec7c l\u1eb7p \u0111i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n kho\u1ea3ng 500 calo so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u0103ng c\u00e2n d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng <strong>calo<\/strong> c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n xu\u1ed1ng kho\u1ea3ng 500 calo\u00a0d\u01b0\u1edbi\u00a0m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00e3y nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac di truy\u1ec1n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n l\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u BMR v\u00e0 TDEE c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n &#8211; h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading--level3 brand-color \"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n (BMR) l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4201\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4201\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4201 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/bmr-4.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/bmr-4.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/bmr-4-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/bmr-4-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/bmr-4-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/bmr-4-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/bmr-4-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4201\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ngay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c b\u1ed5 sung, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 suy ngh\u0129, th\u1edf, ti\u00eau h\u00f3a ho\u1eb7c b\u01a1m m\u00e1u quanh c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ho\u1eb7c BMR (Basal Metabolic Rate) c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i, gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh, chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi di truy\u1ec1n, thu\u1ed1c men v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.bmi-calculator.net\/bmr-calculator\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u00ednh BMR tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn<\/a>\u00a0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\">T\u1ed5ng\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><span style=\"caret-color: #009fc2;\">ti\u00eau<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\">\u00a0hao n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y (TDEE) l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4174\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4174\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4174 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tong-tieu-hao-nang-luong-hang-ngay-1.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tong-tieu-hao-nang-luong-hang-ngay-1.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tong-tieu-hao-nang-luong-hang-ngay-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tong-tieu-hao-nang-luong-hang-ngay-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tong-tieu-hao-nang-luong-hang-ngay-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tong-tieu-hao-nang-luong-hang-ngay-1-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tong-tieu-hao-nang-luong-hang-ngay-1-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4174\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u1ed5ng ti\u00eau hao n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed7i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i b\u1ed9 quanh nh\u00e0, ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft xe bu\u00fdt hay n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y th\u00eam n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u1ec1u calo h\u01a1n.\u00a0S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1eb1ng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb theo d\u00f5i th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c (nh\u01b0 Apple Watch ho\u1eb7c Fitbit) ho\u1eb7c b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111eo thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb theo d\u00f5i nh\u1ecbp tim khi b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch th\u00eam s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y do t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c v\u00e0o BMR c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00fang l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 T\u1ed5ng chi ti\u00eau n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ho\u1eb7c TDEE &#8211; t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 calo m\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y nhi\u1ec1u calo h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Sinh nhi\u1ec7t Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng Kh\u00f4ng T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c (NEAT) \u2013 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1ecf m\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trong su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 b\u1ed3n ch\u1ed3n, l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u theo \u0111i\u1ec7u nh\u1ea1c ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ee9ng thay v\u00ec ng\u1ed3i. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, trong khi c\u1ed9ng BMR v\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng nhau s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 TDEE, th\u00ec c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n cao h\u01a1n nh\u1edd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng NEAT c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading--level3 brand-color \"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>\u0102n bao nhi\u00eau Calo \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n?<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4193\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4193\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4193 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/an-bao-nhieu-de-giam-can-1.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/an-bao-nhieu-de-giam-can-1.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/an-bao-nhieu-de-giam-can-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/an-bao-nhieu-de-giam-can-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/an-bao-nhieu-de-giam-can-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/an-bao-nhieu-de-giam-can-1-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/an-bao-nhieu-de-giam-can-1-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4193\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0102n bao nhi\u00eau Calo \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb chung \u0111\u1ec3 <strong>gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/strong> l\u00e0 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c th\u00e2m h\u1ee5t calo kho\u1ea3ng 500 &#8211; 1.000 d\u01b0\u1edbi TDEE c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y calo h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 \u00edt calo h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee1 d\u1ef1 tr\u1eef hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1eebng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p &#8211; h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1.200 calo m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb l\u00e0 \u00edt h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo m\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n.\u00a0Calo l\u00e0 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0N\u1ebfu l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c<strong> gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/strong> v\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean thon g\u1ecdn h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 trang web c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo cho m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0Nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn r\u1ea5t l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y chung cho nam gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 2.500 v\u00e0 cho ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef l\u00e0 2.000.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau <strong>gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh<\/strong> s\u1ebd v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 1.300 &#8211; 1.500 calo \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef v\u00e0 1.800 &#8211; 2.000 calo \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nam gi\u1edbi.\u00a0N\u1ebfu m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n cao h\u01a1n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y khi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading--level3 brand-color \"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Calo trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1ee9c \u0103n<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4176\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4176\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4176 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/xac-dinh-calo-trong-thanh-phan-thuc-an-1.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/xac-dinh-calo-trong-thanh-phan-thuc-an-1.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/xac-dinh-calo-trong-thanh-phan-thuc-an-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/xac-dinh-calo-trong-thanh-phan-thuc-an-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/xac-dinh-calo-trong-thanh-phan-thuc-an-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/xac-dinh-calo-trong-thanh-phan-thuc-an-1-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/xac-dinh-calo-trong-thanh-phan-thuc-an-1-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4176\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Calo trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1ee9c \u0103n <\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n l\u1ea5y t\u1eeb si\u00eau th\u1ecb s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u tr\u00ean bao b\u00ec ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed9p \u0111\u1ef1ng. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 b\u00e1nh sandwich, \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c b\u00e1t sa l\u00e1t \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i s\u1eb5n v\u00e0o gi\u1edd \u0103n tr\u01b0a, nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo trong b\u1ea3ng \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c m\u1eb7t sau. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1ef1 ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn b\u1eefa \u0103n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfm l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo cho t\u1eebng m\u00f3n (v\u00ed d\u1ee5: m\u1ed7i l\u00e1t b\u00e1nh m\u00ec c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi t\u1eebng m\u00f3n nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 trang tr\u00ed).\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i, b\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ki\u1ec3m tra l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn (ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ki\u1ec3m tra\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.nhs.uk\/live-well\/healthy-weight\/calorie-checker\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo n\u00e0y t\u1eeb NHS<\/a>\u00a0) ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng theo d\u00f5i b\u1eefa \u0103n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 MyFitnessPal.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111i \u0103n ngo\u00e0i, nhi\u1ec1u chu\u1ed7i nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng li\u1ec7t k\u00ea th\u00f4ng tin dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u00ean trang web c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong b\u1eefa \u0103n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p class=\"heading heading--level3 brand-color \"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng Calo hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4178\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4178\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4178 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tan-dung-calo-hieu-qua-1.png\" alt=\"Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, th\u1ee9c \u0103n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tan-dung-calo-hieu-qua-1.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tan-dung-calo-hieu-qua-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tan-dung-calo-hieu-qua-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tan-dung-calo-hieu-qua-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tan-dung-calo-hieu-qua-1-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tan-dung-calo-hieu-qua-1-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4178\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng Calo hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 trong th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o kh\u00e1ch quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ea7n \u0103n &#8211; nh\u01b0ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u01b0 nhau.\u00a0Dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o calo kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u00a0M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m &#8216;t\u1ed1t&#8217; hay th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m &#8216;x\u1ea5u&#8217;, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c nhau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n no l\u00e2u h\u01a1n, t\u1eeb t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n cho bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ti\u1ebfp theo ho\u1eb7c cung c\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u vitamin v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n. th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5, trong khi \u0111\u1ed3 ng\u1ecdt c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 calo v\u00e0 rau xanh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 calo s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u0129a l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7y \u1eafp. rau xanh b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.\u00a0V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cao trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn c\u1ee7a k\u1eb9o, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng vitamin, kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 t\u1eeb rau c\u1ee7.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady,\u00a0ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh\u00a0nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u \u00f4 liu, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t v\u00e0 b\u01a1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 cao, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n no l\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch, m\u1ee9c cholesterol v\u00e0 gi\u00fap cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c vitamin tan trong ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o. A, D, E v\u00e0 K<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo trong ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c b\u1eefa \u0103n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1edbi protein n\u1ea1c, ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, ng\u0169 c\u1ed1c nguy\u00ean h\u1ea1t, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y v\u00e0 rau ngon. B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n ngon v\u00e0 chi\u00eau \u0111\u00e3i, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang xung quanh k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1eefa \u0103n l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Calo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t calo, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2nCalo l\u00e0 g\u00ec, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t calo, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng c\u00e2n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><em><strong>Xem th\u00eam<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/bai-tap-giup-giam-can-nhanh-giam-mo-bung-nhanh\/\">B\u00e0i t\u1eadp gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n nhanh, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee1 b\u1ee5ng nhan